    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. The Test conditions factor achieved level 2 against a required level of 3 due to single-rate testing per ASTM F1717; however, the overall body of evidence — including two-laboratory experimental confirmation, quantitative E/uval metrics below 1.96 for all QoIs, and percent differences below 10% — is sufficient to support an Accepted determination at Medium assurance level for this Class II device application.",
